Weather Data Visualizer
Data Analysis & Visualization Project

This project focuses on working with real-world weather datasets using Pandas, NumPy, and Matplotlib.
You will clean data, compute statistics, visualize trends, and generate meaningful insights.

ğŸ“˜ Project Overview

The goals of this project are to:

Load and inspect real weather datasets

Clean missing or inconsistent data

Process date/time columns

Compute statistical summaries using NumPy

Create multiple weather-related visualizations

Group and aggregate data for deeper insights

Export results and tell a data-driven story

This project demonstrates practical skills useful in data analysis, data science, and Python visualization.

